ed="T" n="0785a03"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0785a03"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000028066"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>蘄</sic><corr>黃</corr></choice><ptr target="#n1691"/>州黃崗山</placeName><persName key="A010662">法普</persName>傳（<persName key="A010664">休靜</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0785a04"/><persName key="A010662">釋法普</persName>，姓<name>潘</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000015064">廬江</placeName>人也。貌古情寬，擁敗<lb
ed="T" n="0785a05"/>納觀方。<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020606" notAfter-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name>中</date>，因見<placeName key="PL000000028066">黃崗</placeName>山色奇秀，其峯<lb
ed="T" n="0785a06"/>巉崪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1634"/>，其林欝密，中有石壇，平坦而高峙。乃放<lb
ed="T" n="0785a07"/>囊挂錫，于中班荊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1635"/>。久之，尋附樹架蓬茨，僅<lb
ed="T" n="0785a08"/>容身而已。未幾，有人自小徑而至，見<persName key="A010662">普</persName>驚<lb
ed="T" n="0785a09"/>怪，問云：「何緣至此？」曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010662">某</ref>本行山麓，見巔頂<lb
ed="T" n="0785a10"/>騰漲，紫氣盤紆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1636"/>可愛，意此山有尤物，故來<lb
ed="T" n="0785a11"/>耳。」諦視<persName key="A010662">普</persName>，遲迴而去。山下行者聞而尋焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0785a12"/>禪學之徒，不數年遽盈百數。<persName key="A010662">普</persName>却之曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010662">老<lb
ed="T" n="0785a13"/>僧</ref>獨居，無物利人，君等亦無所乏。」由是星<lb
ed="T" n="0785a14"/>居之庵多矣。弟子<persName key="A010663">廣嚴</persName>等構成大院，禪客翕<lb
ed="T" n="0785a15"/>如<ptr type="glossary" target="#g768"/>，傳其法者無算。一日，集眾辭云：「<ref type="person" target="#A010662">吾</ref>其終<lb
ed="T" n="0785a16"/>矣。汝曹善住珍惜！」加趺坐胡床而卒。其身<lb
ed="T" n="0785a17"/>不壞散，後以香泥塗<anchor xml:id="beg0785001"/>繢<anchor xml:id="end0785001"/>之。至<date notBefore-iso="+0874-12-21" key="j20406372042521" notAfter-iso="+0880-02-17"><name>乾符</name>中</date>，重<lb
ed="T" n="0785a18"/>立碑頌云。次<placeName key="PL000000023593">洛京華嚴寺</placeName><persName key="A010664">釋休靜</persName>，不知何<lb
ed="T" n="0785a19"/>許人也。屬<persName key="A009489">洞山</persName>禪道風行，<persName key="A010664">靜</persName>往造<ref type="person" target="#A009489">之</ref>，抉擿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1637"/><lb
ed="T" n="0785a20"/>所疑，若雷復于本位焉。北返於<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛邑</placeName>，開演<ptr target="#n1694"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0785a21"/>因赴內齋，諸名公皆執經諷讀，唯<persName key="A010664">靜</persName>并其徒<ptr target="#n1695"/><lb
ed="T" n="0785a22"/>俱默坐。<ref type="person" target="#A006575">帝</ref>宣問：「胡不轉經？」詶答響應，仍皆<lb
ed="T" n="0785a23"/>屬對，悅可帝情<ptr target="#n1692"/>。尋迴<placeName key="PL000000005710">平陽</placeName>示滅。收舍利，四<lb
ed="T" n="0785a24"/>處樹浮圖<ptr target="#n1693"/>。勅諡<persName key="A010664">寶智大師</persName>，塔號<placeName key="PLG00000000092">無為</placeName>也。</p>
